result.adr_address: 731 Nathan Rd, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 731 Nathan Rd, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: The Live House

reviews.text:
Food in general is okay but the portion is rather small. Also the beverages are too expensive. 
The live band never showed up, this was quite disappointing. We were told that the restaurant is not featuring live bands anymore.

Terrible food!!! The side dishes of the pig knuckle had already gone bad and the waiter didn't do anything when we told them, not even a single apology, not to mention the portion of the dish was very small. If u pay the same price at a different restaurant, the pork knuckle normally is double the size. It also took ages for them to make the French fries and guess what? Worst I've ever had. The live music performer has a good voice but he doesn't know how to sing and the music was way too loud. Will never ever come back again, such a waste of money!!!

Food is nice but the price of beverage is way too high... atmosphere is not match with the TV show... TV showing not a local TV, is mainland china one and you know what I mean. The singer is playing hard for his show and he sings not bad
Staffs are nice but always forget what did they answered to do...
if the food is not nicer than expected, there will be only 1 star for that
Love their fried chicken wings. Nice music, great for chilling out. P.S. Temporary system meltdown, cash only.
Raw food, ughhhh

result.adr_address: 香港旺角彌敦道731號
result.name: The Live House

reviews.text:
之前已經到過這間餐廳好幾次， 記得第一，兩次印象比較好， 之後有一次來的時候無論服務態度和食物質素都不好， 但今次因為臨急臨忙，所以沒有太多選擇又來到這裏。 當晚點了拿破崙意粉$128， 汁燒帆立貝$36， 火炙吞拿魚沙律$128， 炸薯條配車打芝士醬$88， 千島海鮮批$148，house red$76，mojito $98x2， 再開一支紅酒$298。 ⭕拿破崙意粉算是咁多款比較好的， 但又不講得上好吃， 一般般吧。 ⭕汁燒帆立貝只有兩隻，留給朋友們吃，所以不知味道如何。 ⭕火炙吞拿魚沙律的吞拿魚過熟， 沙律菜一般。 ⭕炸薯條配車打芝士醬， 薯條偏乾， 車打芝士醬沒有味道的，最後都是要點茄汁吃。 ⭕千島海鮮批， 這件薄餅除了吃到千島醬的味道之外， 都沒有其他評語了。 ⭕House red 的味道比較酸。 ⭕mojito， 朋友說這杯的酒味太少。 ⭕另外再開多一支紅酒味道比較好了， 起碼沒有之前house red的酸味。

整體而言這類的食物大致上普通，餐廳人手不足，點菜的時候叫了很久才有店員過來， 幸好店員的態度也很有禮貌，起碼比起上次好得多，後來埋單的時候店員還給了我們折扣。
這個豬排飯很好味，不過刀叉都要看看從隔離自取,刀都要問才有!

Food in general is okay but the portion is rather small. Also the beverages are too expensive. 
The live band never showed up, this was quite disappointing. We were told that the restaurant is not featuring live bands anymore.

Terrible food!!! The side dishes of the pig knuckle had already gone bad and the waiter didn't do anything when we told them, not even a single apology, not to mention the portion of the dish was very small. If u pay the same price at a different restaurant, the pork knuckle normally is double the size. It also took ages for them to make the French fries and guess what? Worst I've ever had. The live music performer has a good voice but he doesn't know how to sing and the music was way too loud. Will never ever come back again, such a waste of money!!!
